Package com.bewsoftware.utils.struct

package com.bewsoftware.utils.struct
These classes are basically just structs. They are easy to use containers of one or more primitives, and possibly other classes.

The primary use of these classes is to pass a class as a parameter that can be used to return one or more values. They can also be used to get primitive values out of lambda expressions.
